Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.23,00:02:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高清电影网 http://M1080.com 提供字幕下载
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.50,00:00:55.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛尔克影业公司\N
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.94,00:01:00.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导演:保罗.韦尔霍文\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.31,00:01:04.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔.道格拉斯\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:08.83,00:19:12.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如不是作者呢？ 假设是别人看到这本书？\NSo,what if it's not the writer? What if it's someone who read the book?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:14.44,00:19:17.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你面对一位疯狂的杀手…\NYou're dealing,then, with someone so obsessed...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.44,00:19:21.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论是男女 会杀害一切不相关的人…\Nthat he or she is willing to kill an irrelevant and innocent victim...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:21.68,00:19:24.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只为了嫁祸给本书作者\Nin order to place the blame on the person who wrote that book.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:24.85,00:19:28.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种深藏在内心里的仇恨…\NI'm talking about a deep-seated obsessional hatred...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:28.72,00:19:31.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于人命毫不尊重\Nand an utter lack of respect for human life.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:37.79,00:19:42.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们遇到一位千载难逢 世间少见的疯子\NSo,we got a once in a lifetime, top of the line looney-tuney.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:42.57,00:19:44.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这个意思吗？\NThat's what you're saying, right,Doc?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:46.20,00:19:49.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个凶手十分危险…\NYou're dealing with someone very dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:49.67,00:19:52.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且变态\Nand very ill.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:56.68,00:20:00.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明知不可能的. 你根本没有具体证据\NYou know there's no case here. You've got no physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:00.58,00:20:03.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没有不在场证明\NShe hasn't got an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:03.22,00:20:06.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也没动机. 相信我的话…\NShe hasn't got a motive,either. Believe me...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.22,00:20:08.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辩护根本会打得我们 无招架之力\Nher defense would just beat us to death with this copycat thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:09.13,00:20:12.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看过这本书的人都有嫌疑\NAnybody who read the book could have done it.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:12.60,00:20:16.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你打算什么都不做？ -我们叫她来问话\N- What do you want to do now? Nothing? - We call her in for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:16.87,00:20:18.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有的是钱， 我们根本弄不过--\NShe's got enough money to burn the department down...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:18.90,00:20:22.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是最后一位见到死者的人\NShe was the last person seen with the guy.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:22.51,00:20:24.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切由我负责\NI'll take the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:25.18,00:20:27.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了\NIt's yours.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.35,00:20:30.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样没用的\NIt won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:30.85,00:20:33.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会找个明星律师辩护…\NShe'll just waltz in with some superstar lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:33.22,00:20:35.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是浪费纳税人的钱\Nwho'll get us all canned for wasting the taxpayers' money.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:36.12,00:20:38.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她一定会那样做. -不会的\N- That's exactly what she'll do. - No,she won't.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.79,00:20:43.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为她不会找律师\NI don't think she'll hide behind anybody.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:44.09,00:20:46.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她谁都不用找\NI don't think she's gonna hide at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:46.26,00:20:49.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许她跟你一样神经，柯伦\NThen she's as crazy as you are,Curran.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:01.32,00:49:02.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确\NHilarious.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:04.79,00:49:08.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-艾索是我的朋友. -你的朋友把一家人全宰了\N- Hazel's my friend. - Your friend took out her whole family.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:08.80,00:49:11.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她使我了解杀人的冲动\NYes,she helped me understand homicidal impulse.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:12.30,00:49:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校就学到了\NI thought you would have learned that at school.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:15.67,00:49:17.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是理论上的\NOnly in theory.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:17.67,00:49:22.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对杀人冲动了解十分透彻. 不是吗，枪手？\NBut you know all about homicidal impulse,don't you,shooter?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:25.48,00:49:27.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是理论，是实务的\NNot in theory,in practice.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:54.95,01:43:56.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后永远逍遥自在吗？\Nand live happily ever after?
Dialogue: 0,01:43:56.99,01:43:58.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少来了！\NOh,man!
Dialogue: 0,01:44:11.03,01:44:13.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么进来的？\NHow'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,01:44:13.70,01:44:15.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,01:44:15.60,01:44:18.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定再给你一次机会\NI decided to give you a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:18.77,01:44:22.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我想你. -我才刚走你就想我\N- I missed you. - I wasn't gone long enough.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:23.01,01:44:25.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想我吗？\NDid you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,01:44:25.11,01:44:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:37.03,01:44:40.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来告诉我你不想我\NWhy don't you come over here and tell me no.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:43.83,01:44:45.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看过了。- 是吗？\N- I've seen them before. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,01:44:46.10,01:44:48.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再多看几眼吗？\NWell,you might not see them again.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:49.00,01:44:51.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的书快完成了\NMy book's nearly finished.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:51.14,01:44:53.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书中探长也快死了\NMy detective's almost dead.
Dialogue: 0,01:44:53.64,01:44:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以吸最后一根烟吗？\NSo I've got time for a last cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,01:44:55.28,01:44:56.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事后再说\NAfterwards.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:09.59,01:45:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天早上要作些研究\NI've got to do some research tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:12.23,01:45:15.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研究我很在行，我来帮你\NI'm good at research. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:15.23,01:45:17.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用，谢了\NNo,thanks.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:17.17,01:45:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算研究什么？嗯...\NWhat are you researching? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,01:45:21.10,01:45:23.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替你的书找新的结局\Na new ending to your book.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:23.74,01:45:26.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？怎么弄？\NOh,really? What's the twist?
Dialogue: 0,01:45:26.84,01:45:30.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探长爱上不该爱的女人\NThe detective falls for the wrong girl.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:30.85,01:45:33.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他没死\NBut he doesn't die.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:35.28,01:45:38.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他结果怎样了？\NSo what happens to him?
Dialogue: 0,01:45:39.55,01:45:42.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不停疯狂的做爱…\NThey fuck like minks, raise rug rats...
Dialogue: 0,01:45:43.03,01:45:44.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远过着幸福的日子\Nand live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:46.56,01:45:48.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不会畅销\NIt won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:49.60,01:45:50.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,01:45:52.73,01:45:55.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总得有人死掉\NSomebody has to die.
Dialogue: 0,01:45:57.74,01:45:59.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,01:46:00.64,01:46:03.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天天有人死\NSomebody always does.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:20.60,01:46:22.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，我找嘉纳大夫\NMorning. I'm looking for a Dr. Garner.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:22.86,01:46:26.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经不在这里工作了. 她好象去旧金山警局\NShe doesn't work here anymore. She's in San Francisco with the police.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:26.74,01:46:28.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找的是他丈夫\NActually,I'm looking for her husband.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:28.30,01:46:31.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他也在这里工作吧？ -约瑟夫嘉纳？\N- He works here too,doesn't he? - Dr. Joseph Garner?
Dialogue: 0,01:46:31.71,01:46:33.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他？\N- She married? - You know him?
Dialogue: 0,01:46:33.61,01:46:36.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他五六年前就去世了\NHe died about five or six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:36.38,01:46:40.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么死的？ -中弹身亡\N- How did he die? - He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:42.55,01:46:44.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:44.69,01:46:48.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他下班走路回家\NHe was walking home from work.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:48.59,01:46:50.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住所离办公室很近\NHe only lived a couple of blocks from the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:50.93,01:46:52.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人开车经过射死她\NSomebody just drove by and shot him.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:52.69,01:46:56.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是谋杀吗？ -点三八左轮手枪\N- What was the murder weapon? - Revolver,.38. Unrecovered.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:56.33,01:46:58.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-小心些. -有疑犯吗？\N- Watch yourself. - Were there any suspects?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:28.25,00:49:31.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卷入其中的滋味如何？\NWhat happened? Did you get sucked into it?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:31.75,00:49:34.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无法自拔吗？\NDid you like it too much?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:36.52,00:49:39.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在说什么\NI don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:41.30,00:49:43.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谈谈可卡因吧，尼克\NTell me about the coke,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,00:49:45.80,00:49:48.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了观光客的那天…\NThe day you shot those two tourists...
Dialogue: 0,00:49:48.84,00:49:50.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吸了多少可卡因？\Nhow much coke did you do?
Dialogue: 0,00:49:54.58,00:49:57.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以告诉我\NCome on,you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:03.75,00:50:07.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我吸了. -你吸了…\N- I didn't. - Yes,you did.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:07.66,00:50:10.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没替你检验\NThey never tested you,did they?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:11.13,00:50:13.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风纪组的人知道\NInternal Affairs knew.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:16.13,00:50:19.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老婆也知道，对不对？\NYour wife knew too,didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,00:50:24.51,00:50:26.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道怎么回事\NShe knew what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:29.64,00:50:31.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你离火焰太近了\NI think you got too close to the flame.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:39.62,00:50:41.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你很喜欢\NI think you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,00:50:46.33,00:50:48.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才自杀\NThat's why she killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:04.38,00:51:06.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，海伦\NHi,hon.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:10.42,00:51:13.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位见过面\NYou two have met,haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:22.46,00:51:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会是位了不起的角色\NYou're gonna make a terrific character,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:34.71,00:51:38.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正在打电话，马上会叫你\NShe's on the phone. She'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:38.68,00:51:43.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我马上会打回去给你. -探长，你不能进去--\N- I'm gonna have to call you back. - Detective,you can't go in...
Dialogue: 0,00:51:43.38,00:51:45.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁动过我的档案？ -你在说什么？\N- Who's got access to my file? - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:45.79,00:51:47.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁动过我那些档案？\NWho has access to my goddamn file?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:48.16,00:51:51.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人动过. 那些是机密的个人心理资料\NNobody. It's a confidential psychiatric record. It would be illegal.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:51.86,00:51:54.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干的，少对我扯谎言\NDon't you fucking lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,00:51:54.63,00:51:56.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是风纪组动的\NIt was Internal Affairs,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:51:56.70,00:51:57.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\NNo,please.
Dialogue: 0,00:51:57.80,00:52:00.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是谁？ -是尼尔森\N- Who? - It's Nilson.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:12.61,00:52:14.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干，柯伦？\NWhat do you want,Curran?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:14.45,00:52:15.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的档案卖了\NYou sold her my file,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:15.78,00:52:17.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁？\NWho are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:18.09,00:52:21.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳楚梅. 她付你多少？\NCatherine Tramell. How much did she pay you?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:21.59,00:52:25.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点住手\NHey,Curran,come on! Damn it,stop it!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:25.19,00:52:26.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱？\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,00:52:28.63,00:52:32.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手，柯伦！\NHey,back off! Back off,Curran!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:32.53,00:52:35.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻松一点\NNice and easy now. Nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:35.67,00:52:38.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你妈的头，你完蛋了\NYou fucked yourself,shooter. You hear me? You are out!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:38.67,00:52:41.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-柯伦，轻松点. -你死定了！\N- Curran,take it easy. - You are out!
Dialogue: 0,00:52:42.84,00:52:44.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧\NSave it,save it.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:47.82,00:52:50.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-尼克，你没事吧？ -我没事\N- What's going down,Hoss? - Nothing. I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:52:50.42,00:52:53.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们不会放过你的. -我痛恨被人耍着玩\N- They're gonna want your badge. - I'm tired of being played with.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:10.76,01:35:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-想喝咖啡自己来. -谢了\N- Help yourself to some coffee. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,01:46:59.10,01:47:02.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有疑犯，没有动机. 无头悬案\NNo suspects,no motive. Unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:02.70,01:47:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的太太有嫌疑吗？\NWas his wife ever a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,01:47:06.64,01:47:09.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约一年前也有人来问过\NOne of your guys was down here from Frisco a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:09.75,01:47:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他问了同样的问题\NHe was asking the same,exact thing.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:12.25,01:47:14.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我怎么回事吗？\NYou mind telling me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,01:47:14.25,01:47:16.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例行公事\NRoutine.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:16.85,01:47:18.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是那样说的\NThat's exactly what he said.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:18.85,01:47:21.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你又来说是"例行公事"\NNow I got two of you guys telling me it's "routine."
Dialogue: 0,01:47:21.86,01:47:24.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得那家伙的名字吗？\NYou remember what the other guy's name was?
Dialogue: 0,01:47:25.36,01:47:29.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不记得.我想不能确认\NNo. I can't really say that I do.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:29.70,01:47:32.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔森？\NNilsen?
Dialogue: 0,01:47:32.27,01:47:34.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，正是\NYeah. That was it.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:36.74,01:47:39.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她曾经是疑犯吗？ -没有\N- So was she ever a suspect? - No.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:40.58,01:47:41.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有些闲言闲语\NThere was some talk.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:41.88,01:47:43.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一直没有证据\NBut it never panned out.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:44.01,01:47:46.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说些什么？ -女人\N- What kind of talk? - Girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:47.22,01:47:49.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有别的女人？\NHe had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,01:47:49.55,01:47:50.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:52.69,01:47:54.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她有女人\NShe did.
Dialogue: 0,01:47:56.36,01:47:59.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我所说，没有证据\NBut like I said, it never panned out.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:01.90,01:48:04.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢. -希望对你有帮助\N- Thank you. - Hope that helped you out.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:04.77,01:48:08.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，你帮了大忙\NYes,you did. You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:39.03,01:48:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你\NI missed you.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:42.67,01:48:43.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弄完我的研究\NI finished my research.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:43.84,01:48:47.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我的书写完了. -故事是怎么结尾的呢？\N- I finished my book. - So how does it end?
Dialogue: 0,01:48:48.34,01:48:50.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过了\NI told you.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:50.58,01:48:52.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她杀了他\NShe kills him.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:54.98,01:48:57.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，尼克\NGood-bye,Nick.
Dialogue: 0,01:48:58.79,01:49:00.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见？\NGood-bye?
Dialogue: 0,01:49:00.99,01:49:03.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我的书写完了\NYeah. I finished my book.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:06.56,01:49:08.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听见吗？\NDidn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,01:49:08.73,01:49:10.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人物死了\NYour character's dead.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:12.30,01:49:13.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\NGood-bye.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:18.04,01:49:20.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在等什么，送花吗？\NWhat do you want,flowers?
Dialogue: 0,01:49:20.31,01:49:22.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你一本我亲笔签的书\NI'll send you an autographed copy.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:24.61,01:49:26.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干嘛，你在开什么玩笑\NWhat is this, some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,01:49:31.82,01:49:33.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在玩游戏吗？\NYou playing a game here?
Dialogue: 0,01:49:34.29,01:49:36.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了\NThe games are over.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:37.79,01:49:39.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:39.56,01:49:43.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是本世纪最轰动的书，枪手\NIt was the fuck of the century, shooter.
Dialogue: 0,01:49:57.11,01:49:58.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过去\NI'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:26.04,01:50:27.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳楚梅大学一年级的室友\NCatherine Tramell's roommate, freshman year?
Dialogue: 0,01:50:28.04,01:50:31.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚接到她电话，她在奥克兰. 快上车\NI just got a call from her. She's in Oakland. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,01:50:34.32,01:50:36.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找了他宿舍的朋友 找了一整天\NI've been phoning people from her dorm all day.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:36.35,01:50:37.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概知道我想联络到她\NShe must've heard I was trying to reach her.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:14.73,01:35:17.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这下真的搞糊涂了\NI don't understand what the hell is going on here.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:17.73,01:35:19.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那么困难. 这个纯朴的农家女孩…\NIt ain't hard,Hoss. This young farm girl...
Dialogue: 0,01:35:20.04,01:35:23.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认为大家都偏爱她的弟弟们…\Ngot tired of all that attention going to her little brothers...
Dialogue: 0,01:35:23.64,01:35:25.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆把他们做了\Nso she fixed them.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:25.88,01:35:28.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如艾索把一家子全做了\NJust like old Hazel Dobkins fixed her whole family.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:28.88,01:35:31.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是小洛茜当时没结婚礼物\NExcept young Roxy,here, didn't use a wedding present.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:31.75,01:35:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用老爸的剃刀\NShe used daddy's razor.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:43.09,01:35:44.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在明白她们坐在营火前…\NSure makes you wonder what they talk about...
Dialogue: 0,01:35:45.06,01:35:48.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在聊些什么\Nwhen they sit in front of the campfire at night.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:48.16,01:35:51.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他那几个无辜的朋友\NYou ever met a friend of hers that hasn't killed somebody?
Dialogue: 0,01:35:51.77,01:35:54.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为天下女孩都一样\NMust of beat your ordinary, every day girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:54.80,01:35:57.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不大确认是她干的\NI'm not sure,anymore,she did it.
Dialogue: 0,01:35:57.24,01:35:59.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说谁？\NWhich one we talking about now?
Dialogue: 0,01:35:59.64,01:36:02.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道是艾索干的， 小洛茜也干过\NWe know Hazel did it. We know young Roxy did it.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:02.81,01:36:04.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个呢--\NAnd the other one...
Dialogue: 0,01:36:04.18,01:36:09.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的BB欲火难消， 把你的脑袋都烤焦了\NShe's got that magna cum laude pussy that fried up your brain.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:28.80,01:36:31.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"欧伯曼…马克…唐纳."\N"Oberman,Mark W., Donald M."
Dialogue: 0,01:36:32.27,01:36:33.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，没有"丽莎"\NSorry,no "Lisa."
Dialogue: 0,01:36:33.88,01:36:36.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定吗？\NYou sure about the year?
Dialogue: 0,01:36:36.71,01:36:39.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楚梅是八三年毕业的\NCatherine Tramell graduated in '83.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:39.75,01:36:43.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说丽莎也是同一年\NShe said Lisa Oberman was here at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:46.06,01:36:47.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，有楚梅\NYeah,we have Tramell.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:50.70,01:36:52.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有丽莎欧伯曼\NBut no Lisa Oberman.
Dialogue: 0,01:36:52.90,01:36:55.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定没搞错吗？\NAre you sure? There can't be a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,01:36:57.07,01:36:59.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是你搞错了\NOnly if you're making it,Detective.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:14.12,01:37:16.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾索，这是我说过的尼克\NHazel,this is Nick. I told you all about him.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:16.85,01:37:18.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是艾索达普金斯\NNick,this is Hazel Dobkins.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:18.99,01:37:21.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个开枪的\NYou're the shooter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:21.16,01:37:23.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:23.19,01:37:25.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，可以谈一下吗？\NFine,thank you. Can I speak to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:26.00,01:37:30.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-甜心，你去车里等我. -我马上过去\NHoney，Would you wait for me in the car? I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:31.77,01:37:33.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，枪手\NGood-bye,shooter.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:35.04,01:37:37.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢和凶手鬼混\NYou like to hang out with murderers,or what?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:37.94,01:37:41.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道洛茜是-- -我当然知道\N- You know that Roxy was involved... - Yes,of course,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:41.11,01:37:44.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我写的都是不寻常的人…\NI write about unusual people, and sometimes when I do my research...
Dialogue: 0,01:37:44.08,01:37:46.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候为了研究他们必须如此\NI get involved with them.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:46.79,01:37:48.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的情形也一样\NIt happened with you.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:50.19,01:37:53.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人和抽烟不一样\NKilling isn't like smoking.
Dialogue: 0,01:37:53.09,01:37:55.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以戒掉\NYou can quit.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:38.02,01:50:42.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说她知道 凯瑟琳和丽莎何伯曼的底细\NSays she knows all about Catherine and Lisa Hoberman.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:44.59,01:50:45.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？\NYou feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,01:50:47.96,01:50:49.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事\NHere's something else.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:49.73,01:50:53.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼巴兹的心理医生 在凡内士有个办公室\NJohnny Boz's psychiatrist has an office on Van Ness.
Dialogue: 0,01:50:53.13,01:50:54.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜看他和谁共用那办公室？\NGuess who he shares space with?
Dialogue: 0,01:50:55.00,01:50:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伊丽莎白嘉纳大夫\NDr. Elizabeth Garner.
Dialogue: 0,01:51:00.71,01:51:04.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是怎么一回事？\NWhat in the hell's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,01:51:17.03,01:51:20.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在405号房\NI'll be in suite 405.
Dialogue: 0,01:51:22.06,01:51:24.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要上哪去？ -和你一起去呀\N- Where the hell you going? - I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,01:51:24.67,01:51:26.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在休假\NYou're on leave,Hoss.
Dialogue: 0,01:51:26.60,01:51:29.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会去很久的\NIt ain't gonna take long.
Dialogue: 0,01:53:51.91,01:53:53.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动！\NFreeze!
Dialogue: 0,01:53:53.28,01:53:54.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干嘛？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,01:53:54.95,01:53:56.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你他妈的手举起来！\NPut your fucking hands up!
Dialogue: 0,01:53:56.89,01:53:58.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加斯在我留言机上留言要会我\NI got a message to meet Gus here.
Dialogue: 0,01:53:58.89,01:54:01.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他在哪里？ -别动，叫你别动！\N- Where is he? - Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,01:54:01.16,01:54:03.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你先生是怎么回事！ 你仍然是女同性恋吗，贝丝？\NI know about your husband! You still like girls,Beth?
Dialogue: 0,01:54:04.96,01:54:08.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么？ -把你的手从口袋里拿出来！\N- What? - Take you hands out of your pocket!
Dialogue: 0,01:54:08.66,01:54:10.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-把手拿出来！ -你是怎么了？\N- Take them out! - What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,01:54:10.97,01:54:12.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手拿出来！\NTake them out!
Dialogue: 0,01:54:32.22,01:54:34.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\NI loved you.
Dialogue: 0,01:54:50.74,01:54:52.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天！\NOh,God!
Dialogue: 0,01:55:15.73,01:55:18.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会以为她有枪？\NWhat made you think she had a gun?
Dialogue: 0,01:55:19.80,01:55:23.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跑到这里来干嘛？ 加斯在这做什么？\NWhat was she doing here? What was Gus doing here?
Dialogue: 0,01:55:26.98,01:55:28.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组长\NLieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,01:55:56.90,01:55:58.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人\NOne of ours.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:01.11,01:56:03.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:03.81,01:56:06.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得去搜贝丝的住所\NWe'll have to check Beth's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:09.35,01:56:10.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点三八口径的左轮枪\NThirty-eight caliber revolver.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:11.05,01:56:13.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏在书架上\NIn the bookcase, behind some books.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:16.26,01:56:19.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查查它是不是杀尼尔森那把枪\NHave ballistics check it for Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:19.56,01:56:22.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好进来看一下\NLieutenant. You better come in here.
Dialogue: 0,01:56:51.26,01:56:53.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想大致是这样了\NI guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:09.24,01:57:13.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是. 所有证据都不利于伊莉莎白嘉纳\NDefinitely not. We feel all the evidence points to Dr. Elizabeth Garner.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:13.92,01:57:15.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们查过了，是她的尺寸没错\NWe checked. It's her size.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:15.98,01:57:18.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在楼梯听到你声音 就把假发扔了\NShe probably heard you on the stairway and dumped this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:18.22,01:57:19.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有405\NThere's no suite 405.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:20.02,01:57:21.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳楚梅的大一室友…\NCatherine Tramell's freshman roommate is dead.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:22.02,01:57:23.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两年前就因血癌去世了\NShe died of leukemia two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:24.03,01:57:26.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是她的死亡证明. -莎莉娜如何？\N- Here's a fax of her death certificate. - What about Salinas?
Dialogue: 0,01:57:26.83,01:57:29.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗.等等，杰克！\NYeah,hold on. Jack!
Dialogue: 0,01:57:31.27,01:57:33.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去尼尔森办公室 找过嘉纳的档案没？\NDid you check Nilsen's office for any files on Beth Garner?
Dialogue: 0,01:37:57.79,01:38:00.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\NI gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,01:38:01.26,01:38:03.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证六点前一定会回家\NI promised I'd get her home by 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,01:38:03.71,01:38:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太喜欢“美国头号通缉犯”\NShe just loves "America's Most Wanted."
Dialogue: 0,01:38:06.20,01:38:09.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在柏克莱时 根本没丽莎这个人\NThere was no Lisa Oberman when you were at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,01:38:09.97,01:38:13.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在调查我吗？\NWhat are you doing? Checking up on me?
Dialogue: 0,01:38:13.21,01:38:16.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？ 我说的是"何伯曼"\NFor what? I said "Hoberman."
Dialogue: 0,00:01:07.15,00:01:11.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,片名:本能\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.52,00:01:14.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗.斯通\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.00,00:01:20.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔治.杜德拉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:23.50,00:01:24.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮.翠普莱伦\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.47,00:01:57.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服装设计:艾伦.米洛维奇\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.27,00:02:02.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐制作:杰里.戈德史密斯\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.71,00:02:08.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化妆:罗伯.伯顿\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:10.08,00:02:12.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,编辑:佛兰克.伍斯吉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.39,00:02:17.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕设计:特伦斯.马奇\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:19.39,00:02:21.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄影导演:简.德.邦特\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:30.57,00:02:32.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剧本:乔.伊斯特哈斯\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.41,00:02:37.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制片:阿兰.马修\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:33.59,00:04:35.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-早安，探长. -给我两个探长的镜头\N- Good morning,Detective. - I want a shot of the two detectives.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.59,00:04:37.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后\NKeep it back,folks.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:37.76,00:04:39.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好. -早上好\N- Howdy. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.13,00:04:44.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面\NUp there.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:48.54,00:04:50.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行的如何？\N- How's it going,Gus? - Morning,Pete.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:50.77,00:04:54.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这小子是谁？ -强尼巴兹，是摇滚歌手\N- Who was this fucking guy? - Rock and roll,Gus. Johnny Boz.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:55.15,00:04:57.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-从没听说过. -这还用说\N- Never heard of him. - Before your time,cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:57.58,00:04:59.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-朗尼，他在哪里？ -楼上右手边房间\N- Hey,Ronny,where they hiding? - Upstairs,to the right.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:59.85,00:05:03.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在六十年代中期有过几首畅销曲子， 在菲尔摩街上有间俱乐部\NMid '60s,had five or six hits. Got a club down on Fillmore now.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:03.65,00:05:05.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有了\NNot now,he don't.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:06.59,00:05:08.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者在何时死亡的？\N- Do we have a time of death? - Almost.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:08.83,00:05:11.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是托卡组长\N- Do you guys know Captain Tallcott? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:11.30,00:05:14.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-署长怎么也来了？ -来视察\N- What's the Chief's office doing here? - Observing.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.67,00:05:20.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-法医官，怎样？ -92度，大约6小时前\N- What's it say,Doc? - Ninety-two degrees. About six hours.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:20.70,00:05:23.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡时间约在凌晨两点左右\NPuts time of death at around 2:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:23.31,00:05:26.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把那边窗帘拉上\NCan somebody close the drapes over there?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.74,00:05:29.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约1小时前女佣发现的尸体\NMaid came in about an hour ago and found the body.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.38,00:05:31.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她不是住客. -或许是女佣干的\N- She's not a live-in. - Maybe the maid did it.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.85,00:05:34.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她五十四岁，体重两百四十磅\NShe's 54 years old and weighs 240 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.39,00:05:36.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-尸体没有淤伤. -不是女佣干的\N- No bruises on the body. - It ain't the maid.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:37.09,00:05:38.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天知道\NNever know.
