Dialogue: 0,01:32:02.34,01:32:04.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一向喜欢看着我做爱\NShe wanted to watch me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,01:32:11.61,01:32:15.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她试图杀你，对不对？\NShe tried to kill you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,01:32:15.79,01:32:20.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你喜欢她看你吗？ -你以为我叫她去杀你吗？\N- Did you like her to watch you? - You think I told her to kill you?
