Dialogue: 0,01:39:46.60,01:39:49.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就那么一次\NIt was just that one time.
Dialogue: 0,01:39:49.97,01:39:52.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她开始迷恋我\NShe developed a fixation on me.
