Dialogue: 0,01:40:01.08,01:40:03.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是这样告诉你的？\NIsn't that what she told you?
Dialogue: 0,01:40:03.99,01:40:06.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说是你\NShe said it was you.
