Dialogue: 0,01:42:08.11,01:42:10.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？她现在怎样\NOh,you did? What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,01:42:13.58,01:42:16.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算告诉我\NYou're not going to tell me what she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:16.29,01:42:19.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们到底在玩什么游戏. -我也是在玩\N- I thought we were done playing games. - I did too.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:19.86,01:42:21.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说你缠着她不放\NShe said you got it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:21.69,01:42:24.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把头发染的和她一样\NShe said you styled your hair like she did.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:24.56,01:42:26.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信她\NAnd you believed her.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:27.66,01:42:33.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾去校园警局检举她\NI had to go to the campus police and file a report about her.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:33.30,01:42:36.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你八成认为人是我杀的？\NI suppose you still think I kill people too?
Dialogue: 0,01:42:38.06,01:42:40.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\NNo！
Dialogue: 0,01:42:41.08,01:42:42.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说谎\NLiar.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:46.62,01:42:50.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你说是哪里？ -旧金山凶杀组\N- Who'd you say you're with? - Homicide,San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:52.96,01:42:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里\NHere we go.Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:57.19,01:42:59.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确有人报案检举丽莎何伯曼， 是在八零年一月\NThere was a report about Lisa Hoberman, January,1980.
Dialogue: 0,01:42:59.90,01:43:02.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但不在这里. -谁拿去了？\N- But it's out of here. - Who's got it?
Dialogue: 0,01:43:03.63,01:43:05.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的人…尼尔森\NOne of your guys. Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:05.73,01:43:08.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-认识他？ -认识\N- You know him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:08.10,01:43:10.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\NThanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:10.34,01:43:13.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他拿回来. 他拿走一年了\NTell him to bring it back. He's had it a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:13.78,01:43:16.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔森拿了档案又怎样 你也不知道里面写什么\NSo Nilsen had a report on Beth. You don't know what was in it.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:33.57,01:57:37.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柏克森那没有任何警方档案\NNo police report from Berkeley. Nothing at all about Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:37.27,01:57:40.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我\NI'm back.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:40.14,01:57:41.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:42.01,01:57:45.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专家说那把点三八口径的左轮枪 与尼尔森的伤口吻合\NBallistics says the.38 we found in her apartment was used on Nilsen.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:45.35,01:57:47.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有登记\NNo registration. They're checking with Salinas.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:47.85,01:57:50.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰锥和巴兹那案子的凶器 既同牌又同型\NThe ice pick was the same brand and model as the Boz weapon.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:50.85,01:57:53.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查过了嘉纳住所和办公室的电话录音--\NChecked the tape machines at Dr. Garner's apartment and office...
Dialogue: 0,01:57:53.19,01:57:54.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部的办公室\Nboth here and the one on Van Ness.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:54.86,01:57:56.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加斯没在任何地方留言\NThere's no message from Gus on any of them.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:56.29,01:57:58.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她公寓里的录音机没有用过\NThe tape in her apartment was unused.
Dialogue: 0,01:57:58.36,01:58:01.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼巴兹的心理医生说…\NJohnny Boz's psychiatrist says he thinks he remembers...
Dialogue: 0,01:58:01.16,01:58:04.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他记得嘉纳和巴兹是一年前…\NDr. Garner and Boz meeting at a Christmas party at his house.
Dialogue: 0,01:58:04.57,01:58:06.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他家举行的圣诞派对中认识的\NA year ago.
Dialogue: 0,01:58:09.24,01:58:12.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心莫测，对不对？\NYou just can't tell about people, can you?
Dialogue: 0,01:58:13.98,01:58:18.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是上过床的女人\NEven the ones you think you know inside and out.
Dialogue: 0,01:58:21.58,01:58:24.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜，柯伦\NCongratulations,Curran.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:23.91,01:59:25.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了…\NI heard about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:28.02,01:59:30.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电视播了\NOn TV.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:41.93,01:59:45.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能对你用情\NI can't allow myself to care about you.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:48.94,01:59:51.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能对…\NI can't allow myself...
Dialogue: 0,01:59:51.77,01:59:54.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人用情\Nto care.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:57.58,01:59:59.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这么做的\NI don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,01:59:59.95,02:00:02.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这么做的\NPlease. I don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,02:00:04.15,02:00:06.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了所有的人\NI lose everybody.
Dialogue: 0,02:00:07.02,02:00:09.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去你\NI don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,02:01:55.56,02:01:57.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在怎么办，尼克？\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,02:01:59.03,02:02:02.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命做爱…\NFuck like minks...
Dialogue: 0,02:02:02.70,02:02:06.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象老鼠一样快乐的活下去\Nraise rug rats and live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,02:02:17.15,02:02:18.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌老鼠\NI hate rug rats.
Dialogue: 0,02:02:21.69,02:02:24.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那拼命做爱好了，别想老鼠了…\NFuck like minks, forget the rug rats...
Dialogue: 0,02:02:24.69,02:02:27.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的生活下去\Nand live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:16.95,01:43:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-凯瑟琳告诉我了. -她说的话能信吗\N- Catherine told me what was in it. - If she's telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:19.58,01:43:21.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加斯，你还不明白吗？\NGus,don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,01:43:21.25,01:43:23.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝丝杀了强尼陷害凯瑟琳…\NIf Beth killed Johnny Boz to frame Catherine...
Dialogue: 0,01:43:23.25,01:43:25.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怕别人知道柏克赖的往事！\Nshe wouldn't want anybody to know what happened in Berkeley!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:25.25,01:43:28.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但被尼尔森发现了，使她有动机杀他\NBut Nilsen found out about it. That gives her the motive to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,01:43:28.56,01:43:31.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么知道尼尔森发现了？\NHow did she know Nilsen found out, if it happened?
Dialogue: 0,01:43:31.59,01:43:33.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是风纪组长，或许他去问她！\NHe probably asked her!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:33.96,01:43:36.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一点也不象是神经病！\NShe'd have to be nuttier than a 20 pound fruitcake!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:36.63,01:43:39.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不象是连环杀人狂！\NShe's not the one who hangs out with multiple murderers!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:39.57,01:43:41.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是你女朋友干的！ -她是作家，那是她的工作！\N- You're girlfriend is! - She's a writer! That's her job!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:42.07,01:43:45.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不信 柏克莱一定有人知道真相\NI don't buy it. There must be somebody at Berkeley who knows what happened!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:45.24,01:43:47.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道真相！凯瑟琳说的！\NI know what happened! Catherine told me!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:47.24,01:43:50.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我都去查过了！    - 你真的是...\N- Everything she says has checked out! - You got tweety birds...
Dialogue: 0,01:43:50.58,01:43:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 操B操昏头了！\Nfluttering around in your head!
Dialogue: 0,01:43:52.68,01:43:54.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为你可以随便乱搞\NYou think you can fuck like minks, raise rug rats...

